<para style="q1">

<verse number="31" style="v" />The law of his God is in his heart;</para>

<para style="q1">his feet will not slip.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="32" style="v" />The wicked person watches the righteous person</para>

<para style="q1">and seeks to kill him.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="33" style="v" />Yahweh will not abandon him into the evil person's hand</para>

<para style="q1">or condemn him when he is judged.</para>
